#: ../C/gnome-access-guide.xml:384(para)
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Mouse button click</guilabel> emulates the currently selected "
"mouse button. Pressing <keycap>/</keycap>, <keycap>*</keycap> or <keycap>-</"
